# Title: Pubprn.vbs Proxy Execution
# Author: frack113
# Date: 2022-05-28
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects the use of the 'Pubprn.vbs' Microsoft signed script to execute commands.
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.stealth, attack.t1216.001
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_lolbin_pubprn.yml

CommandLine="*\\pubprn.vbs*" CommandLine="*script:*"